fields.description:
The following exception appears at the bottom of the "Files" tab of build plans, under certain conditions:

{noformat}
Expression build.buildDefintion is undefined on line 68, column 18 in viewBuildFiles.ftl
{noformat}

As currently supplied, the postCommitBuildTrigger.sh script yields the following error on some platforms (e.g. Ubuntu):

{noformat}
postCommitBuildTrigger.sh: 22: 1: not found
{noformat}

This can be rectified by editing the first line to read:

{noformat}
#! /bin/bash
{noformat}

We should also check other triggering scripts.
